title: The Carnival Cruise Ship That Spread Coronavirus Around the World
itunes:title: The Carnival Cruise Ship That Spread Coronavirus Around the World
description:
How were hundreds of infected Ruby Princess passengers allowed to disembark in Sydney and return to homes from Tasmania to Florida?

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.
